{"thag1.80:0.1":"Theragatha 1.80 ","thag1.80:0.2":"Ekakanipata ","thag1.80:0.3":"Atthamavagga ","thag1.80:0.4":"Uggattheragatha ","thag1.80:1.1":"“Yam maya pakatam kammam, ","thag1.80:1.2":"appam va yadi va bahum; ","thag1.80:1.3":"Sabbametam parikkhinam, ","thag1.80:1.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo”ti. ","thag1.80:1.5":"… Uggo thero … ","thag1.80:1.6":"vaggo atthamo. ","thag1.80:2.0":"Tassuddanam ","thag1.80:2.1":"Vacchapalo ca yo thero, ","thag1.80:2.2":"atumo manavo isi; ","thag1.80:2.3":"Suyamano susarado, ","thag1.80:2.4":"thero yo ca piyanjaho; ","thag1.80:2.5":"Arohaputto mendasiro, ","thag1.80:2.6":"rakkhito uggasavhayoti. "}